Name: Julia Lu (jlu97)

Special instructions:

I added a bunch of debug messages but disabled them by default.
To enable them, build with the debug target in the Makefile. 
Enabling them slowed down the programs, like the snake demos, a lot.

Other things: 
Since the pdf isn't very clear on what to do if system calls fail
for internal helper functions, I chose to treat it as fatal and
exit the whole program.

I changed the include for fp.h from angle brackets to quotes so its
found during compilation.


